{"tid":619732,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"越南美女小學教師成熱話　網民：爸爸都去接放學","createTime":"2018-04-07T02:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T03:31:43.000Z","uid":81228,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4b72a2ac6be5cddc3a4f4f264eebe6bce8d1b3eb","tid":619732,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/f/f451019e7a689b4908124539802b15ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2Ff%2Ff451019e7a689b4908124539802b15ec.jpg&h=3f474e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要數到東南亞盛產美女的地區，越南一定佔有一席，當地美女長相出眾外，還帶有一種淡淡的清純風，最近一名越南小學女教師熱爆台灣網絡，她身材平均，加上臉蛋甜美，不少網民都笑言學生們的爸爸全都去接子女放學了。<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/f/ff3cde459a2454b368b2a52409d8a887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2Ff%2Fff3cde459a2454b368b2a52409d8a887.jpg&h=f74c2335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />instagram 相片<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/7/7e99dd1e8c5b614f5d8820bd79652170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F7%2F7e99dd1e8c5b614f5d8820bd79652170.jpg&h=a9fc9e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/f/fb45936f4597c7d7f53624f03dbbc80c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2Ff%2Ffb45936f4597c7d7f53624f03dbbc80c.jpg&h=c114870b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年 28 歲的越南小學教師 THU&Yacute; NG&Acirc;N 擁有圓大的眼睛、高挺的鼻樑，長相甜美可愛，身材亦十分均勻，加上越南女孩身上散發的獨有清純氣質，更是引人注意，雖然她鎖骨位置有一行紋身，但仍然無損她的吸引力。<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/1/15d6e633a9a0e2372bd2dec7c8fc6549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F1%2F15d6e633a9a0e2372bd2dec7c8fc6549.jpg&h=8b26a1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/9/938662ac16f6c630ed891516ed30b06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F9%2F938662ac16f6c630ed891516ed30b06b.jpg&h=22d4a30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/0/08b5f3ca1d4e8fc74bb86a2f1292464b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F0%2F08b5f3ca1d4e8fc74bb86a2f1292464b.jpg&h=a67a376d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身為小學教師的 THU&Yacute; NG&Acirc;N 似乎與一眾小朋友關係良好，有時更會在社交平台分享與學生們的合照，有這麼一位美豔動人的老師，難怪網民們都笑言，小朋友的爸爸都會爭相接送子女上下課。<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/a/a78871e87f271f829acfa9f159de1514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2Fa%2Fa78871e87f271f829acfa9f159de1514.jpg&h=5368707f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/1/17067652a34128ac32d1acf2913dc959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F1%2F17067652a34128ac32d1acf2913dc959.jpg&h=dedcf3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/f/ff0e563f702e716984c0c01e4a8f08bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2Ff%2Fff0e563f702e716984c0c01e4a8f08bb.jpg&h=ed2eed78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時 THU&Yacute; NG&Acirc;N 的 Instagram 和 Facebook 上分別有 1.1 萬和 8.7 萬人追蹤，想了解她的生活日常的話，不妨追蹤一下，成為她的粉絲吧！<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/f/ff4fe20f487c808f5cfb040ce442dbb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2Ff%2Fff4fe20f487c808f5cfb040ce442dbb8.jpg&h=2b4e274c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/9/9e819e6d2538298b3164c108e81ffdd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F9%2F9e819e6d2538298b3164c108e81ffdd7.jpg&h=9ea11196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/04/06/6/6022dbb956e9946e6869ff3ff6a2c17f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F6%2F6022dbb956e9946e6869ff3ff6a2c17f.jpg&h=2614a8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180406/1/67/1/%E8%B6%8A%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8-%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E6%88%90%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E9%83%BD%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%BE%E5%AD%B8-8683184.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F1%2F67%2F1%2F%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E7%2588%25B8%25E7%2588%25B8%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AD%25B8-8683184.html&d=S3axBjbT7DzXQv2YFLyEHTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5812c8f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180406/1/67/1/%E8%B6%8A%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8-%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E6%88%90%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E9%83%BD%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%BE%E5%AD%B8-8683184.html</a>"},{"pid":"24a4b812becdf56621c154cc61034607cf915072","tid":619732,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"好文好圖 多謝分享"},{"pid":"9ba60b312d1cb6ac84d55750e5bcf813c7abecdd","tid":619732,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"香港代表都大把"},{"pid":"abc858adef5662c004ac25dbf10e42a2f80b2294","tid":619732